{"tid":277140,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我懷疑屋企有👻","createTime":"2017-06-09T11:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T16:36:00.000Z","uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"218fc2848f4bc18698d87d702a60736e03cdf3b9","tid":277140,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"琴晚瞓教發夢有個未見過嘅女人從後擒住我,又係咁用手指篤我塊面,我就用口咬佢手指,之後fing甩左佢<br />\n<br />\n跟住醒左,聽到房嘅收音機聲,但冇開眼<br />\n當時我就側身向右瞓,諗住再瞓返,發返同一個夢,去揸個女人波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n接近瞓著個陣feel到有人從後咁搭隻手埋黎放我膊頭同頸之間,我好自然咁用右手捉住隻手,feel到係冰涼,跟著再feel到背後有個頭貼住我,我用手去捉,感覺好似捉住一個人額頭對上嘅頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,咁我放返手,個人唔敢郁住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時我唔敢開眼,但肯定係清醒,之後慢慢瞓返平個人,又冇再feel到野,諗起聽日要返工就繼續瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47f788720c720feb250034df1b60cce7e988ad3","tid":277140,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:07:52.000Z","msg":"為何喝過那咖啡杯無故失蹤了"},{"pid":"954c677eeae16c9b3033a5c195f5b083fc3a7643","tid":277140,"uid":48434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"家裡卻彷彿增添了數本新書"},{"pid":"a64d7270a4eaad508317c63ebe1155347970c5d7","tid":277140,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:16:42.000Z","msg":"波都渣過 下次屌佢屌到貼貼服服啦"},{"pid":"cdaae366425894f457e208c6eb44c1c20314646e","tid":277140,"uid":68014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:19:54.000Z","msg":"召   咒怨圖"},{"pid":"5b1465b22015812f0eb0ac78d097ff7c69f4c8f4","tid":277140,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"唔開眼點知有冇揸錯阿妹對波？"},{"pid":"3839187ef7b9bc454efa75bcfde0decfb82b37a1","tid":277140,"uid":38267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:22:07.000Z","msg":"加甜唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces